<br>
Combine in a jewelers' kit...<br>
<br>
Silver bar and bloodstone.<br>
Trivial at 26<br>
<br>
Silver and jasper.<br>
Trivial at 30<br>
<br>
Silver and star rose<br>
Trivial at 34<br>
<br>
Silver and topaz<br>
Trivial at 44<br>
<br>
Electrum bar and turquoise.<br>
Trivial at 79<br>
<br>
Electrum bar and bloodstone.<br>
Trivial at 87<br>
<br>
Electrum and jasper.<br>
Trivial at 92<br>
<br>
Electrum bar and star rose.<br>
Trivial at 98<br>
<br>
Electrum bar and Jade<br>
Trivial at 106<br>
<br>
Electrum bar and topaz.<br>
Trivial at 111<br>
<br>
(Now the most expensive part)<br>
Gold bar and malachite.<br>
Trivial at 146<br>
<br>
Gold bar and Turquoise.<br>
Trivial at 151<br>
<br>
Gold bar and Hematite.<br>
Trivial at 154<br>
<br>
Gold bar and Canelliean.<br>
Trivial at 167<br>
<br>
Gold bar and Star Rose.<br>
Trivial at 170<br>
<br>
Gold bar and Jade.<br>
Trivial at 178<br>
<br>
Gold bar and Pearl.<br>
Trivial at 180<br>
<br>
**edit**<br>
Gold Bar and Topaz<br>
Trivial at 183<br>
<br>
Gold Bar and Peridot<br>
Trivial at 185<br>
<br>
Gold Bar and Opal<br>
Trivial at 191<br>
<br>
Gold Bar and Star Ruby<br>
Trivial at 199<br>
<br>
<br>
If you want to lessen the cost of this skill even more you can do so by hunting for the gems. It will be more time consuming but a lot easier on your bank. Jasper and Bloodstone drop in Lavastorm off of the lava crawlers. Star rose quartz is also dropped in Lavastorm as well as Najena and Eurd's Crossing. Turquoise is dropped in Steamfront. Jade is dropped in WC off of lesser mummies, both Guk's, and desert Madmans in both South Ro and Oasis.  Topaz is dropped off of Hill Giants, Griffons, Spectre's, Minotaur's in Steamfront, and the Goblin Warlord in Warslik Woods.Canellians are off of Fire Elemental's in Lavastorm, Goblin Spirit Callers, and Goblin Warlords.<br>
<br>
